                        browser type, IP address, device information, and data on how you interact with our website.
                      </p>
                      <p class="text-base text-white mb-24p">
                        <span>1.3 Cookies and Tracking:</span> We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to
                        enhance your user experience, remember your preferences, and analyze website traffic.
                      </p>
                    </div>

                    <div id="use-information">
                      <h3 class="text-32 text-white my-24p">2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
                      <p class="text-base text-white mb-24p">
                        <span>2.1 Service Provision:</span> We use your personal information to deliver and improve our
                        services, process transactions, and communicate with you regarding your account and our
                        offerings.
