                      <p class="text-base text-white mb-24p">
                        <span>2.2 Marketing and Communications:</span> With your consent, we may use your contact
                        information to send you promotional materials, updates, and newsletters about our services.
                      </p>
                      <p class="text-base text-white mb-24p">
                        <span>2.3 Analytics and Improvement:</span> We analyze user behavior and trends to improve our
                        website, develop new features, and enhance the user experience.
                      </p>
                      <p class="text-base text-white mb-24p">
                        <span>2.4 Legal Compliance:</span> We may use your information to comply with legal obligations,
                        enforce our Terms and Conditions, and protect our rights.
                      </p>
                    </div>

                    <div id="sharing-information">
                      <h3 class="text-32 text-white my-24p">3. Information Sharing and Disclosure</h3>
                      <p class="text-base text-white mb-24p">
                        <span>3.1 Third-Party Service Providers:</span> We may share your information with third-party
                        providers that assist us in delivering our services, such as payment processors, analytics
                        providers, and marketing agencies. These third parties are obligated to handle your information
                        securely and only use it for the specific purposes of providing services to us.
                      </p>
                      <p class="text-base text-white mb-24p">
                        <span>3.2 Business Transfers:</span> In the event of a merger, acquisition, or sale of all or
                        part of our assets, your information may be transferred as part of the transaction. We will
                        notify you of any changes to data ownership or usage rights in such cases.
                      </p>
                      <p class="text-base text-white mb-24p">
                        <span>3.3 Legal Requirements:</span> We may disclose your information if required by law or in
                        response to legal processes, such as subpoenas or court orders, to comply with applicable legal
                        or regulatory obligations.
                      </p>
                      <p class="text-base text-white mb-24p">
                        <span>3.4 Protection of Rights:</span> We may disclose your information to protect the rights,
                        property, or safety of our company, our users, or others. This includes cooperating with third
                        parties to prevent fraud or address security issues.
                      </p>
                    </div>

                    <div id="user-rights">
                      <h3 class="text-32 text-white my-24p">4. Your Rights and Choices</h3>
                      <p class="text-base text-white mb-24p">
                        <span>4.1 Access and Update:</span> You have the right to access, update, or correct your
                        personal information at any time by accessing your account settings or contacting our support
                        team.
                      </p>
                      <p class="text-base text-white mb-24p">
                        <span>4.2 Opt-Out:</span> You can opt out of receiving promotional communications from us by
                        following the unsubscribe instructions provided in any communication or by contacting us
                        directly.
                      </p>
                      <p class="text-base text-white mb-24p">
                        <span>4.3 Data Deletion:</span> You may request the deletion of your personal information by
                        contacting our support team. Please note that we may retain certain data to fulfill legal
                        obligations or resolve disputes.
                      </p>
                      <p class="text-base text-white mb-24p">
                        <span>4.4 Cookie Preferences:</span> You can manage your cookie preferences through your browser
                        settings, allowing you to accept, reject, or limit cookies. Disabling cookies may affect your
                        experience with some features on our website.
                      </p>
                    </div>

                    <div id="security">
                      <h3 class="text-32 text-white my-24p">5. Security Measures</h3>
                      <p class="text-base text-white mb-24p">
                        <span>5.1 Data Encryption:</span> We employ industry-standard encryption technologies to protect
                        your personal information during transmission and storage.
                      </p>
                      <p class="text-base text-white mb-24p">
                        <span>5.2 Access Control:</span> Access to your personal information is restricted to authorized
                        personnel who need it to perform their job duties, ensuring that only essential personnel have
                        access to your data.
                      </p>
                      <p class="text-base text-white mb-24p">
                        <span>5.3 Regular Audits:</span> We conduct regular security audits and vulnerability
                        assessments to maintain the security of our systems and protect your data.
                      </p>
                      <p class="text-base text-white mb-24p">
                        <span>5.4 Incident Response:</span> In the event of a data breach, we have a comprehensive
                        incident response plan in place. We will take steps to contain and minimize any impact, and
                        affected users will be notified promptly if necessary.
                      </p>
                    </div>

                    <div id="changes-terms">
